  "title": "Sam's Clam and Oyster Bar",
  "description": "After last year’s booming ★★★★★ hit \"Soup and Hogan's\", Sam Daly and Ethan Lang crawl out of their caves with Sam’s Clam and Oyster Bar! A mother-shucking gorgeous musical full of seafood, chaotic romance, and mythological madness. Bring your barrels, they'll be full of laughs.",
  "credits": "<strong>Playwright</strong>: Sam Daly and Ethan Lang<br/><strong>Director</strong>: Elizabeth Janzen<br/><strong>Cast</strong>: Nico Maiorana, Sarah Kyle, Șam Daly, Ethan Lang, Astrid Deibert, Ali Balloun, Ben Healey, Marshall Eglinski<br/><strong>Designers</strong>: Ethan Lang, Elizabeth Janzen and Sam Daly<br/><strong>Stage Manager</strong>: Meg Walker<br/>",
  "website": "https://www.instagram.com/Topbunktheatre",
  "plain_language": "Sam's Clam and Oyster Bar is a comedic musical about a man named Sam who loses his Grandpa and has to run his failing Clam shop. Pearl, the bartender, helps convince Sam not to give up on his dreams when, by chance, a new supplier starts delivering to their shop. With their luck turning towards the better, how will Sam and Pearl keep the greedy townsfolk at bay from eating their whole supply without them turning on the business owners?",
